  "instructions": [
    "Heat 2 tbsp olive oil in a wide paella pan over medium heat.",
    "Sauté onion and garlic for 2 minutes until fragrant.",
    "Add bell peppers and sauté for 5 minutes until tender.",
    "Stir in soaked saffron, bay leaf, black pepper, and sea salt.",
    "Gently mix in 15g chopped makrut lime leaves.",
    "Pour in 400ml creamy coconut milk and cook on low heat for 10 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Remove from heat and let rest for 2 minutes before serving."
